// Must write 2, not 1: BD_SPAWN_SAFANA is a 3-state machine.
// 1 = "Safana in tavern, Coran breakup scene pending" — BD0110.baf
// fires the scene on ==1 and puppets the party's own Safana (PT-3).
// 2 = scene resolved, the only value nothing in BD0110 reacts to.
IF
  Global("BD_SPAWN_SAFANA","BD0110",0)
  InPartyAllowDead("safana")
THEN
  RESPONSE #100
    SetGlobal("BD_SPAWN_SAFANA","BD0110",2)
    Continue()
END
